            <h1 class="mt-4 text-center">What you’ll need:</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 px-5" >
                <ul class="px-5  py-3">
                    <li> South Indian Filter set (including the plunger).</li>
                    <li>18g coffee (approximately 9 teaspoons) in South Indian Filter grind.</li>
                    <li>tablespoon. </li>
                    <li>One Cup.</li>
                    <li>100ml water (⅖ cup) at 95°C (1:30 minutes off boil).</li>
                    <li>One Kettle.</li>
                    <li>Scales, if possible, otherwise follow eye measurements.</li>

                </ul>        
            </p>

        </div> 

       </div>

   </div>
   <div class="container-fluid">
