        <div class="col-lg-6  " style="font-family:'Pacifico', cursive;color:#e5eff7;">
            <h1 class="mt-5 text-center">Brewing Recipe</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 px-5" >
                <ul class="px-5  py-3">
                    <li> Add 18g coffee powder in the upper chamber of the filter.</li>
                    <li>Place it over the lower chamber where the coffee decoction is to be collected.</li>
                    <li>Use the plunger to level the coffee grinds, and leave the plunger on top.</li>
                    <li>Pour 100ml hot water in the top chamber ensuring the plunger stays in place.</li>
                    <li>Place the lid and let it drip through over 9:30 to 10 minutes. </li>
                    <li>Take 50 ml coffee and add 60 ml of hot milk or 50 ml of hot water.</li>
                    <li>Add sugar to your liking.</li>

                </ul>        
            </p>

